long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Inspired by Jed York's unrivaled knack for snatching defeat from the jaws of victory, York This turns any instance of the "f-" word into "York". I would say this makes any open webpage safer for little eyes, but I think I'd rather subject my son to a Quentin Tarantino flick than a Jed York presser. Miss u J Harbs.
